data.description: Welcome!   We (Rutgers Entrepreneurial Society) are hosting our General Interest Meeting for the semester at the Hatchery in Alexander Library, @ 6:30 PM on Friday, January 31st. We will discuss what the Rutgers Entrepreneurial Society stands for, and what you might gain from being a part of it.   2) ALL of our upcoming events for the semester, which will include keynote speakers, valuable skills needed in the field of entrepreneurship, and networking opportunities with some of the most ambitious and successful students at Rutgers so far.   3) Our events will include another year of Rutgers Shark Tank, and a Hackathon.
